{"word":"G2843 - κοινωνικός - koinōnikós - koy-no-nee-kos' - Willing to communicate","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοινωνικός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">koinōnikós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">koy-no-nee-kos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Willing to communicate</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உதாரகுணமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. social, sociable"},{"paragraph":"2. free in giving, liberal"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2844 - κοινωνός - koinōnós - koy-no-nos'/2844\">G2844</a>; <i>communicative</i>, that is, (pecuniarily) <i>liberal:</i> - willing to communicate.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2839/2839\">G2839</a>, <a href=\"#/G2840/2840\">G2840</a>, <a href=\"#/G2841/2841\">G2841</a>, <a href=\"#/G2842/2842\">G2842</a>, <a href=\"#/G2843/2843\">G2843</a>, <a href=\"#/G2844/2844\">G2844</a>, <a href=\"#/G4790/4790\">G4790</a>, <a href=\"#/G4791/4791\">G4791</a>"}]}